      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642900/RenderMan_HoudiniHelp.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433108088&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642900/RenderMan_HoudiniHelp.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433108088&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544642923\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_HoudiniHelp.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642900\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"a590b735-3c5a-46a8-916e-9973cd22e860\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><br/><br/></p><ul><li>RenderMan help: <span class=\"confluence-link\">See <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19662095/RenderMan\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19662095\" data-linked-resource-version=\"10\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">RenderMan</a>.<br/></span></li><li>To get help on the context, hover the mouse over an item such as a parameter to see its tooltip.</li><li>To get help on a shelf tool, hover the mouse over a tool and hit F1.</li><li>Additional resources are linked in the <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFH27/pages/544643524/RenderMan+Menu\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544643524\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">RenderMan Menu</a></li></ul><p>For commercial support, take a quick look at our <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19662089/Getting+Support\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19662089\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Support Page</a> or visit the <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://renderman.pixar.com/forum/forumdisplay.php?s=c5e4564dc722f5247dd5749cbd426724&amp;forumid=169\" rel=\"nofollow\">commercial forum</a>.</p><p><br/></p><p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642900/RenderMan_HoudiniHelp.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433108088&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642900/RenderMan_HoudiniHelp.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433108088&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544642923\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_HoudiniHelp.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642900\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"a590b735-3c5a-46a8-916e-9973cd22e860\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><br/><br/></p><ul><li>RenderMan help: <span class=\"confluence-link\">See <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19662095/RenderMan\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19662095\" data-linked-resource-version=\"10\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">RenderMan</a>.<br/></span></li><li>To get help on the context, hover the mouse over an item such as a parameter to see its tooltip.</li><li>To get help on a shelf tool, hover the mouse over a tool and hit F1.</li><li>Additional resources are linked in the <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFH27/pages/544643524/RenderMan+Menu\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544643524\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">RenderMan Menu</a></li></ul><p>For commercial support, take a quick look at our <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19662089/Getting+Support\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19662089\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Support Page</a> or visit the <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://renderman.pixar.com/forum/forumdisplay.php?s=c5e4564dc722f5247dd5749cbd426724&amp;forumid=169\" rel=\"nofollow\">commercial forum</a>.</p><p><br/></p>"
